      "message": "Would be nice if this (optionally) allowed an int status code to ride along, so that we have some indication of what went wrong. Messages that need to be logged via this interface will almost always come along with a kern_return_t or errno.\n\nYou don’t need to turn the int into a string. A simple decimal or (even easier) hexadecimal conversion would do the trick.",
